ger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"By the One in whose hand is the soul of Muhammad, the parable of the believer is that of a piece of gold. Its owner blows upon it, yet it never changes or diminishes. By\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34839,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/27\/parable-rushing-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":6299,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Parable of one who rushes through prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 27, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Abdullah al-Ash\u2019ari reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, saw a man who did not complete his bowings and rushed through his prostrations while praying. The Prophet said, \u201cIf he were to die in this state, he will have died upon a religion besides that\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28825,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/08\/parable-believer-horse-stable\/","url_meta":{"origin":6299,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Parable of the believer is a horse in a stable","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon, him, said, \u201cThe parable of the believer and faith is that of a horse in its stable. It roams about and then returns to its stable. Verily, the believer becomes negligent and then returns bac